sPenWarning.title: S Pen bug warning
sPenWarning.description: If you are using an S Pen, you may experience a bug where the app will crash when trying to erase with the S Pen button. This is a bug in the Flutter framework, and the fix will likely be released within a month. In the meantime, please use the eraser button in the toolbar.
